      <title>刺激措施推动中国工厂活动意外增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/china-factory-activity-unexpectedly-expands-on-stimulus-boost</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项私人调查显示，尽管有一周的假期，中国上个月的制造业活动仍然意外回升，这是北京出台刺激计划支撑经济后经济企稳的进一步迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-01/china-factory-activity-unexpectedly-expands-on-stimulus-boost</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 01 Nov 2024 01:47:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
